{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ad2c41de05","title":"中央人民政府政务院发布工商业税暂行条例","origin":"根据文件的翻印件打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"98eb3a1fb0","index":0,"year":1950,"month":1,"day":31,"articleId":"ad2c41de05"}],"tags":[{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"edb3c47ed0","type":"title","text":"中央人民政府政务院发布工商业税暂行条例","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"467ff704fc","type":"subtitle","text":"（政务院1950年1月27日第17次政务会议通过，1月31日公布)","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"4637a8447c","type":"subtitle","text":"第一章  总    则","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"d8790be581","type":"paragraph","text":"第一条  凡在本国境内以营利为目的之工商事业，除另有规定者外，不分国籍，不分经营性质，不分公私企业及合作事业，均依本条例之规定，分别计算其营业额及所得额，于其营业行为所在地，征收工商业税。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"ecf4a8e169","type":"paragraph","text":"第二条  工商业依其经营性质，分为固定工商业、临时商业及摊贩业。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"e8aed9a792","type":"paragraph","text":"第三条  具有临时营业性质之行商，以及固定工商业不按所报行业而从事本业以外之经营者，一律按其营业额，征收临时商业税。其征收办法另订之。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"03b3ccc5ba","type":"paragraph","text":"第四条  为管理市场，平衡负担起见，对摊贩营业，应按其超过规定之资本额及经营情况，征课定额之摊贩牌照税。其征收办法另订之。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"1089f70b7b","type":"paragraph","text":"第五条  下列各款免征工商业税：","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"0f9ebe7f7a","type":"paragraph","text":"一、国家专卖、专制事业；","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"0b9c9c5c1c","type":"paragraph","text":"二、贫苦艺匠及家庭副业；","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"bac55d91a0","type":"paragraph","text":"三、非以营利为目的之事业经中央人民政府批准者；","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"6d2e75b228","type":"paragraph","text":"四、其他经中央人民政府批准者。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"1fb30e362e","type":"subtitle","text":"第二章  税  率","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"c73c416af8","type":"paragraph","text":"第六条  工商业税依下列规定，分别按照其营业额及所得额计算征收之：","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"fcbf941c06","type":"paragraph","text":"一、依营业额计算者，税率（甲）按营业总收入额百分之一至百分之三。（乙）按营业总收益额百分之一·五至百分之六；分业计征。（附分业税率表）","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"865ed0a688","type":"paragraph","text":"二、依所得额计算者，税率自百分之五至百分之三十，依所得额按全额累进，分级计征。（附分级税率表）","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"087413a398","type":"paragraph","text":"第七条  下列各款，就其所得计税部分，分别减征：","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"fa984e08f8","type":"paragraph","text":"甲、减征百分之四十者：","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"f4e7c49c0d","type":"paragraph","text":"一、第一类机器制造业；","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"0a9c7c701d","type":"paragraph","text":"二、第一类矿冶业；","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"7fd2f5205a","type":"paragraph","text":"三、电业；","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"4a8111ce8c","type":"paragraph","text":"四、车船制造业。","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"5a9c5c819c","type":"paragraph","text":"乙、减征百分之三十者：","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"bfb66302ab","type":"paragraph","text":"一、第二类机器制造业；","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"9f7dfe1339","type":"paragraph","text":"二、第二类矿冶业；","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"f9084f4e41","type":"paragraph","text":"三、第一类化工制造业；","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"943480522f","type":"paragraph","text":"四、电工器材制造业。","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"44cf0cad05","type":"paragraph","text":"丙、减征百分之二十者：","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"11ecf6908c","type":"paragraph","text":"一、第二类化工制造业；","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"5dc2b80ca1","type":"paragraph","text":"二、农具制造业；","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"74340941d3","type":"paragraph","text":"三、文教卫生用品制造业与出版业；","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"0eed7f957d","type":"paragraph","text":"四、出口商业；","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"a0885900c9","type":"paragraph","text":"五、出口货物制造业；","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"6d3d470c38","type":"paragraph","text":"六、代替外来必需品制造业；","index":33,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"3e00d7f67e","type":"paragraph","text":"七、第一类运输业。","index":34,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"70c1afe873","type":"paragraph","text":"丁、减征百分之十五者：","index":35,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"458d9d5381","type":"paragraph","text":"一、印刷器材制造业；","index":36,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"da0c1441ba","type":"paragraph","text":"二、橡胶皮革制造业；","index":37,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"a3c008c6ed","type":"paragraph","text":"三、建筑器材制造业。","index":38,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"3ab7dd2308","type":"paragraph","text":"戊、减征百分之十者：","index":39,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"93f11242b6","type":"paragraph","text":"一、非机器的交通工具制造业；","index":40,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"87e05b4f14","type":"paragraph","text":"二、手工工具制造业；","index":41,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"2ad39ba61e","type":"paragraph","text":"三、修理机器业；","index":42,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"518b2ca005","type":"paragraph","text":"四、普通必需品制造业；","index":43,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"c865ec6630","type":"paragraph","text":"五、卫生业；","index":44,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"9b8d37782e","type":"paragraph","text":"六、第二类运输业；","index":45,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"231ab4618e","type":"paragraph","text":"七、畜牧业。（附减征行业范围表）","index":46,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"ed08d6efea","type":"paragraph","text":"凡经营对国计民生有特殊利益而为上列各款所未能包括者，得呈请中央人民政府分别酌予减征。","index":47,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"5ea5003ae0","type":"paragraph","text":"第八条  公营企业应纳之工商业税，其属于所得额计算部分者，另按提取利润办法，缴解国库，不再征税。其属于营业额计算部分者，应就地照征。","index":48,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"2fa6f1a105","type":"paragraph","text":"第九条  合作事业应纳之工商业税，其合于合作法之规定者，得酌予减免，征税办法另订之。","index":49,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"917bfc7d74","type":"paragraph","text":"第十条  工厂商店兼营非同—税率之事业，应分别依照其不同税率计征；其琐细不易分别计征者，按其主要行业之税率计征。","index":50,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"54c7cd225b","type":"subtitle","text":"第三章  申报与调查","index":51,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"319483f7c6","type":"paragraph","text":"第十一条  凡工商业，于开业、歇业、转业之二十日前，除依规定向工商管理机关申请登记，领取或缴销营业许可证外，并以副本送税务机关存记。","index":52,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"34632fefae","type":"paragraph","text":"第十二条  工商业应依规定时间，分别将营业额及所得额填具申报表，并检附必需表单，送达税务机关。","index":53,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"5600c217fe","type":"paragraph","text":"第十三条  工商业必须设置日记帐及总帐两种主要帐簿。发生营业行为时，须自他人取得凭证，或开给他人凭证。其凭证与存根必须按月顺序保存，以备税务机关查核。但小本经营之工商业户不在此限。","index":54,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"690ac17118","type":"paragraph","text":"第十四条  税务机关为了解工商业经营及负担情况，有随时派员查询之权，任何工商业者，均应据实报告，不得拒绝或隐瞒。","index":55,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"bc3a11c5da","type":"paragraph","text":"第十五条  税务机关派出执行职务之人员，应出示机关证件，其无证件者，被调查人应拒绝提供帐据，并报请税务机关查究。","index":56,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"a4feabbb0b","type":"subtitle","text":"第四章  计算与征收","index":57,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"7ed6edcbec","type":"paragraph","text":"第十六条  工商业税之营业部分，按营业总收入额或总收益额计算，规定如下：","index":58,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"3ff546302b","type":"paragraph","text":"一、出售产品之工业及贩卖货品之商业，按销货总额，减除销货折扣及销货退回后以销货净额计算之。","index":59,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"e76d14ec9a","type":"paragraph","text":"二、供给劳务或信用之行业，按佣金、报酬金，手续费、汇费、利息、保险费或其他收益额计算之，不得减除任何成本或费用。但保险业之分出保费，应自保险费总额内减除计算。","index":60,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"5e7f923c59","type":"paragraph","text":"第十七条  工商业税之所得部分，其所得额之计算，以其每营业年度或实际经营期间之收入总额，减除各项成本费用及损失后之余额为所得额。前项所称收入总额，包括营业收入与杂项收入。所称成本，系指销货成本或制造成本。所称费用损失，系指销货费用、管理费用、财务费用及其他杂项损失。","index":61,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"35058af351","type":"paragraph","text":"第十八条，为照顾各地工商业之发展程度，经营方法及会计制度，各地税务机关得斟酌实际情形，分别按下列办法计征：","index":62,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"ac9f97fb41","type":"paragraph","text":"一、有健全之会计制度，经税务机关审定认为可资征税确据者，得采用自报实缴方式，配合查帐办法，按其营业额及所得额，依率计征。","index":63,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"8b4161f7c1","type":"paragraph","text":"二、不合前项标准者，得依民主评议方式，依据税率及计算标准，参用调查资料，评定计征。","index":64,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"20294e1819","type":"paragraph","text":"三、采用民主评议之地区，对于特种行业会计制度较为健全者，得分别采用查帐方法计征。","index":65,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"a7be9e3978","type":"paragraph","text":"四、较小单位或城镇，采用查帐与评议均有困难者，得斟酌实际情况，采用定期定额征税办法。","index":66,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"491fca78f2","type":"paragraph","text":"第十九条  纳税义务人应纳税款，属于按营业额计算部分者，每三个月征收一次。属于按所得额计算部分者，每年第二季度终了，由当地税务机关估征一次（估征办法另订），年终结帐后，汇算清缴。","index":67,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"afd53bc27d","type":"paragraph","text":"为简化手续缴纳方便超见，前项分别计算之应纳税额，得合并征收，并得经税务机关之决定，分期预缴。","index":68,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"c08fa4701a","type":"paragraph","text":"第二十条  税务机关征收工商业税，其依营业额计算之应纳税款，每年分一月、四月、七月、十月四次征收缴库。其因特殊情形不能按期办理者，须经税务总局或管理局核准，但不得逾一个月。其因地区惯例或实际情形，可以按月征收或按两个月征收者，得提前办理。","index":69,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"14fd0fd868","type":"paragraph","text":"依所得额计算之应征税款，其估征部分，须于本年度第七月以内完成缴库，年终汇算清缴期限，最迟不得超过次年度第三月。","index":70,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"045e4c0d00","type":"paragraph","text":"第二十一条  因合并、解散、转让、闭歇而歇业之工商业户，应于歇业后五日内，将结算报告当地税务机关，核定应纳税款，即行缴库。","index":71,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"bc8eb75e1f","type":"paragraph","text":"第二十二条  有分红制度之工商业，须先核算提存其应纳税额后，再行分红。","index":72,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"bb7ba1a038","type":"paragraph","text":"第二十三条  工商业税之评议组织，按工商各行业分别选举代表组成。其组织规程另订之。其评议方式：工商业分别评议；各行分别评议；工商兼营者，分别评议，合并征收。","index":73,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"0b3369233a","type":"subtitle","text":"第五章  罚  则","index":74,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"61b84c314b","type":"paragraph","text":"第二十四条  凡违反本条例第十一、第十二、第十三、第十四、第二十一、第二十二各条之规定者，以违章论，处以一百万元以下之罚金。","index":75,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"69a76053a1","type":"paragraph","text":"第二十五条  匿报营业额及所得额者，除追缴其应纳税额外，并处以漏报税额三倍至十倍之罚金。","index":76,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"435c93616e","type":"paragraph","text":"第二十六条  不按期缴纳税款者，除限日追缴外，并按日科以应纳税额百分之三的滞纳金，伪造证据或故意抗税者，得送法院处理。","index":77,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"31bafd6de8","type":"subtitle","text":"第六章  附  则","index":78,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"5a8a33dbb1","type":"paragraph","text":"第二十七条  本条例施行细则另订之。","index":79,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"3044aa96f5","type":"paragraph","text":"第二十八条  本条例施行后，以前各地区对工商业征税之单行办法、单行法令及新解放城市暂时沿用之营业税、特种营业税及营利事业所得税等征收办法，一律废止。","index":80,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"b462508fe2","type":"paragraph","text":"第二十九条  本条例自公布之日施行。","index":81,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"4301f20ffa","type":"paragraph","text":"附表一  依营业额计算分业税率表","index":82,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"f6ba0c7304","type":"paragraph","text":"甲、按营业总收入额计算征收者：","index":83,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"a34c5f8d36","type":"paragraph","text":"一、矿冶业、液体燃料工业、机器制造业、化工制造业、车船制造业、电工器材制造业、面粉制造业、纺织工业——税率百分之一。","index":84,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"597aac2ba7","type":"paragraph","text":"二、制药工业、医疗器材制造业、耐火砖工业、翻砂工业、炼气工业、化学品制造业、印刷业、农具制造业、制糖工业、出口货物制造业、出入口业、水泥制造业、火柴制造业、造纸工业——税率百分之一·五。","index":85,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"55bfb3efd5","type":"paragraph","text":"三、化学原料商业、医药商业、卫生事业之药房部分、米面粮商业、煤炭商业、棉布商业、书报业、文具商业、其他制造业——税率百分之二。","index":86,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"064cf85cbb","type":"paragraph","text":"四、五金电料商业、化妆品制造业、屠宰业——税率百分之二·五。","index":87,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"cdb15d4f84","type":"paragraph","text":"五、纸烟制造业、迷信品制造业、酿造业、中西饮食业、照象业、照象材料业、钟表眼镜业、干鲜货业、其他贩卖业——税率百分之三。","index":88,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"a49081424c","type":"paragraph","text":"乙、按营业总收益额计算征收者：","index":89,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"84fada7879","type":"paragraph","text":"一、公用事业、修理业——税率百分之一·五。","index":90,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"38c5a83c56","type":"paragraph","text":"二、服装商业、量测商业、打捞商业——税率百分之二。","index":91,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"8f6473e7e4","type":"paragraph","text":"三、运输业、浴室理发业、染洗业——税率百分之二·五。","index":92,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"dd3713430a","type":"paragraph","text":"四、堆栈业、包作业——税率百分之三。","index":93,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"474fdb7248","type":"paragraph","text":"五、银钱业、保险业、信托业、旅栈业、广告业、租赁业——税率百分之四。","index":94,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"b95ca2eb34","type":"paragraph","text":"六、银楼业、娱乐业、报关业、喜庆殡葬服务业、典当业——税率百分之五。","index":95,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"acf2095e4f","type":"paragraph","text":"七、房地产代理业、交易所业、牙行业、委托拍卖业、代表经销业——税率百分之六。","index":96,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"b1e4551456","type":"subtitle","text":"附表二  依所得税额计算分极税率表","index":97,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"e42cddba16","type":"paragraph","text":"一、所得额未满一百万元者，课税百分之五。","index":98,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"5ba88a3276","type":"paragraph","text":"二、所得额在一百万元以上未满一百五十万元者，课税百分之六。","index":99,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"b3b445bcc6","type":"paragraph","text":"三、所得额在一百五十万元以上未满二百万元者，课税百分之八。","index":100,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"213fe41764","type":"paragraph","text":"四、所得额在二百万元以上未满三百万元者，课税百分之十。","index":101,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"0d855b5e7a","type":"paragraph","text":"五、所得额在三百万元以上未满四百万元者，课税百分之十一。","index":102,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"6aaf5bbd68","type":"paragraph","text":"六、所得额在四百万元以上未满六百万元者，课税百分之十四。","index":103,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"dba5916799","type":"paragraph","text":"七、所得额在六百万元以上未满八百万元者，课税百分之十六。","index":104,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"49524cc829","type":"paragraph","text":"八、所得额在八百万元以上未满一千万元者，课税百分之十八。","index":105,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"e1b1e108cc","type":"paragraph","text":"九、所得额在一千万元以上未满一千三百万元者，课税百分之二十。","index":106,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"49039e3874","type":"paragraph","text":"十、所得额在一千三百万元以上未满一千六百万元者，课税百分之二十二。","index":107,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"d73e6440b5","type":"paragraph","text":"十一、所得额在一千六百万元以上未满二千万元者，课税百分之二十四。","index":108,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"850807310b","type":"paragraph","text":"十二、所得额在二千万元以上未满二千五百万元者，课税百分之二十六。","index":109,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"8eab774808","type":"paragraph","text":"十三、所得额在二千五百万元以上未满三千万元者，课税百分之二十八。","index":110,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"bf4bb8ba1e","type":"paragraph","text":"十四、所得额在三千万元以上者，一律课税百分之三十。","index":111,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"96a403c7ca","type":"paragraph","text":"注：本表制定时，北京小米价格每斤八百元，上海大米价格每斤八百元。嗣后遇有物价涨落，得由税务总局或区管理局，根据本条例之规定标准，作适度之调整，并报中央财政部备查。","index":112,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"d6b84f66b5","type":"paragraph","text":"第二十四条之罚金数额，亦准用前项规定。","index":113,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"f10b0b583e","type":"subtitle","text":"附表三  依所得额计算减征行业范围表","index":114,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"bff3bfc656","type":"subtitle","text":"减征率        业    别            项    别","index":115,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"010ba57e72","type":"subtitle","text":"百分之四十","index":116,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"596659fe7f","type":"paragraph","text":"第一类机器制造业    动力机、重工作母机、农业机、纺纱机、造纸机。","index":117,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"a94fec1853","type":"paragraph","text":"第一类矿冶业        钢铁、非铁金属、石油。","index":118,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"47f22d2970","type":"paragraph","text":"电业                电力、电灯、电热。","index":119,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"c41f2d27f5","type":"paragraph","text":"车船制造业          火车、汽车、电车、轮船及其重要机械器材。","index":120,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"5623432622","type":"subtitle","text":"百分之三十","index":121,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"936e8e3d40","type":"paragraph","text":"第二类机器制造业    轻工作母机、面粉机、橡胶机、榨油机、织布机、染整机及其他各行业专用机器。","index":122,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"fc6f8447a0","type":"paragraph","text":"第二类矿冶业        煤、矾、云母、石绵、石墨、炼焦。","index":123,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"b0be14810d","type":"paragraph","text":"第一类化工制造业    硫酸、盐酸、硝酸、碱、氧气、肥田粉、石油代用品、比重表、耐高温坩锅、工业用温度表、烧管、烧杯、烧瓶及其他重要化学仪器用品。","index":124,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"d206563253","type":"paragraph","text":"电工器材制造业      电话机、电报机、收音机、电线、电表、变压器。","index":125,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"320de1aaeb","type":"subtitle","text":"百分之二十","index":126,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"26f1b811dd","type":"paragraph","text":"第二类化工制造业    染料、杀虫剂及其他重要化学用品。","index":127,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"a46927eff7","type":"paragraph","text":"农具制造业          水车、犁、铧及新式改良农具。","index":128,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"b4e7cddda8","type":"paragraph","text":"文教卫生用品制造    显微镜、经纬仪、自来水业与出版业  笔、钟表、计算机、电影机、照象机及照象器材、精细绘图仪器及工具、中西各种特效药品、专事出版大众图书之出版业及制造体育用品业。","index":129,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"320a5b39a8","type":"paragraph","text":"出口商业            专事经营出口之贸易业、或经营进出口贸易业之出口部分及轮船运输公司。","index":130,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"86423c1e58","type":"paragraph","text":"出口货物制造业      地毯及地毯毛线、猪鬃、出口植物油、打蛋业、马尾整理业、肠衣整理业、特种工艺业。","index":131,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"e5c16e7f25","type":"paragraph","text":"代替外来必需品制造业    特种纸张、电池、电瓶、玻璃、麻袋、水表、甘油、滑机油、自行车、各种胶、云母纸、汽车油磅垫。","index":132,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"beb2c6f2cb","type":"paragraph","text":"第一类运输业        汽车运输业。","index":133,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"8cfd67317d","type":"subtitle","text":"百分之十五","index":134,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"20c4bd82d1","type":"paragraph","text":"印刷器材制造业      印石胶、铅版、铜版、珂罗版、铅字模、铸字、打字机、腊纸、晒图纸、写版及特制印墨。","index":135,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"68a5dff260","type":"paragraph","text":"橡胶皮革制造业      汽车胎、自行车胎、轮带、水龙带、轮带用革。","index":136,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"2f88f3464a","type":"paragraph","text":"建筑器材制造业      水泥、砖瓦、涵洞、石灰、石绵品、建筑木料。","index":137,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"584be396c3","type":"subtitle","text":"百分之十","index":138,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"d4a587e38e","type":"paragraph","text":"非机器交通工具制造业    大车、手车、木船。","index":139,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"cd9b6f00f9","type":"paragraph","text":"手工工具制造业      弹花弓、轧花机、织丝机及其他重要手工业工具。","index":140,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"5165d31fa2","type":"paragraph","text":"修理机器业          修理各种机器及电镀电焊业、电工业。","index":141,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"aeec14b264","type":"paragraph","text":"普通必需品制造业    棉纱布织染、机制面粉、磨房、瓷器、搪瓷、陶器、玻璃器皿、铜盆、铁锅、铝锅、铝盆、火柴、钮扣、粘版、度量衡器、铜丝罗底、五金、线、针、钉、一般中西药品、一般植物油、一般皮革、一般纸张、文具墨水、印刷等业。","index":142,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"0111c02aed","type":"paragraph","text":"卫生业              医院、诊疗所、施诊所附设之药房部分。","index":143,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"33903ab920","type":"paragraph","text":"第二类运输业        大车运输业、内河船业。","index":144,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"},{"id":"e9f26160fb","type":"paragraph","text":"畜牧业              牛羊乳业、种畜牧场、乳制品制造业。","index":145,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05"}],"page":{"id":"8d8b2241fd","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ad2c41de05","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}